videos.headline: Willis hits the corner 3-pointer for Kentucky

videos.description: 1H (16:16) HOF Rokas Gustys made Dunk. Assisted by Ty Greer.
videos.headline: Hofstra's Gustys left alone for the two-handed dunk
Gustys takes it himself for another Hofstra dunk

videos.description: Isaiah Briscoe knocks down the 3-pointer to continue Kentucky's hot shooting in the first half against Hofstra.
videos.headline: Briscoe continues Kentucky's hot shooting

videos.description: Kentucky head coach John Calipari discusses mistakes in 1st half
videos.headline: Kentucky head coach John Calipari discusses mistakes in 1st half

videos.description: Kentucky has exploded in the second half against Hofstra, punctuated with Edrice Adebayo rocking the rim with a huge two-hand dunk.
videos.headline: Adebayo's massive slam has Kentucky running in second half

videos.description: It's show time for Kentucky with the steal and baseball pass that leads to a monster alley-oop finish for Edrice Adebayo.
videos.headline: Showtime for Kentucky with alley-oop to Adebayo

videos.description: Kentucky guard Brad Calipari wore a "Man Crush Everyday" shirt adorned with the face of coach John Calipari, who is also his father, during warmups before Sunday's game against Hofstra, calling to mind Drake's recent tribute to ESPN's Doris Burke.
